  "local_port": 37464,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Which are the most romantic songs in Malayalam?",
  "response": "Malayalam cinema is celebrated for its melodious and heartfelt romantic songs that have captivated audiences for decades. Whether you're reminiscing about classic hits or exploring contemporary tunes, here's a curated list of some of the most romantic Malayalam songs:\n\n### **Classic Romantic Hits**\n\n1. **\"Manathe Chandanakkeeru\"**\n   - **Movie:** *Nandanam* (2002)\n   - **Singers:** K. S. Chithra, Hariharan\n   - **Composer:** Vidyasagar\n   - *A beautifully composed duet that captures the essence of blossoming love.*\n\n2. **\"Aaromale\"**\n   - **Movie:** *Manichitrathazhu* (1993)\n   - **Singers:** Unni Menon, K. S. Chithra\n   - **Composer:** G. Devarajan\n   - *A timeless classic known for its enchanting melody and poignant lyrics.*\n\n3. **\"Thumbi Vaa\"**\n   - **Movie:** *Olangal* (1982)\n   - **Singers:** K. S. Chithra, M. G. Sreekumar\n   - **Composer:** Ouseppachan\n   - *A soft and soothing track that remains a favorite among romantic song enthusiasts.*\n\n4. **\"Ente Khalbile\"**\n   - **Movie:** *Thoovanathumbikal* (1987)\n   - **Singer:** K. S. Chithra\n   - **Composer:** Bombay Ravi\n   - *A melodious love song that beautifully portrays deep emotions.*\n\n5. **\"Pavizha Mazha\"**\n   - **Movie:** *Athiran* (2019)\n   - **Singers:** Naresh Iyer, Deepak\n   - **Composer:** Gopi Sundar\n   - *A serene and emotional song that resonates with listeners for its heartfelt lyrics.*\n\n### **Contemporary Romantic Favorites**\n\n6. **\"Malare\"**\n   - **Movie:** *Premam* (2015)\n   - **Singer:** Vijay Yesudas\n   - **Composer:** Rajesh Murugesan\n   - *A soulful melody that became an anthem of love for a new generation.*\n\n7. **\"Jeevamshamayi\"**\n   - **Movie:** *Theevandi* (2018)\n   - **Singer:** Vijay Yesudas\n   - **Composer:** Rajesh Murugesan\n   - *A romantic track with heartfelt lyrics and captivating tunes.*\n\n8. **\"Kannil Kannil\"**\n   - **Movie:** *Kunjiramayanam* (2015)\n   - **Singers:** Vijay Yesudas, Jyotsna\n   - **Composer:** Shaan Rahman\n   - *A sweet duet that beautifully expresses love and longing.*\n\n9. **\"Neeye Oli\"**\n   - **Movie:** *How Old Are You* (2014)\n   - **Singer:** Jyotsna\n   - **Composer:** Shaan Rahman\n   - *A heartfelt song expressing deep emotions and affection.*\n\n10. **\"Entammede Jimikki Kammal\"**\n    - **Movie:** *Velipadinte Pusthakam* (2017)\n    - **Singers:** Vineeth Sreenivasan, Ranjith Unni\n    - **Composer:** Shaan Rahman\n    - *While upbeat, it carries a romantic charm that's widely appreciated.*\n\n### **Other Notable Romantic Songs**\n\n11. **\"Thaarame Thaarame\"**\n    - **Movie:** *Kadaram Kondan* (Malayalam Dubbed Version, 2019)\n    - **Singer:** Sid Sriram\n    - **Composer:** Ghibran\n    - *A modern romantic number with a captivating melody.*\n\n12. **\"Vennilave Vennilave\"**\n    - **Movie:** *Minnaram* (1994)\n    - **Singers:** K. S. Chithra, Unni Menon\n    - **Composer:** S. P. Venkatesh\n    - *A classic romantic duet with memorable lyrics.*\n\n13. **\"Munthirithenthi\"**\n    - **Movie:** *Ayalum Njanum Thammil* (2012)\n    - **Singers:** K. S. Chithra, M.R. Rajakrishnan\n    - **Composer:** Bijibal\n    - *A beautiful romantic song with touching lyrics and soothing tunes.*\n\n14. **\"Ee Shishiram\"**\n    - **Movie:** *Pranayakalam* (1993)\n    - **Singer:** K. S. Chithra\n    - **Composer:** Kaithapram Damodaran Namboothiri\n    - *A soothing and romantic track that remains beloved by many.*\n\n15. **\"Nilaave Vaa\"**\n    - **Movie:** *Minsara Kanavu* (1997)\n    - **Singers:** K. S. Chithra, Hariharan\n    - **Composer:** A. R. Rahman\n    - *An enchanting melody with mesmerizing vocals.*\n\n### **Additional Recommendations**\n\n- **\"Ini Njan Onnu Visramikkate\"** from *Neelathamara*\n- **\"Aaradhike\"** (Malayalam Version)\n- **\"Sundariye Vaa\"** from *Happy Wedding*\n- **\"Soul of Home\"** from *Home*\n\nThese songs span various eras of Malayalam cinema, each bringing its unique flavor to the theme of love and romance. Whether you're creating a romantic playlist or simply exploring the rich musical landscape of Malayalam films, these tracks are sure to evoke emotions and memories.\n\nFeel free to revisit these melodies or discover them for the first time to experience the magic of Malayalam romantic music!",
